.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, lemonade, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, sudoku, woodworking
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, poker, domino
1. the person playing domino is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the person playing domino is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing poker##1
6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
7. the person playing domino is between the person playing poker and the person who's hobby is gardening##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | tea      | fanta       | lemonade   |
| Hobby      | gardening   | puzzles  | woodworking | sudoku     |
| Game      | snooker     | domino | poker        | chess |

