.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, cooking, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, spy, western
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, security-guard, project-manager, engineer
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the doctor##1
2. the person watching crime movies is between the engineer and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the project-manager##1
4. the project-manager is on the right of the doctor##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | camping | cooking | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | western | crime   | spy         |
| Job           | doctor | project-manager  | security-guard   | engineer      |

