.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, prince, havana, fonseca
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, photography, woodworking, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, salsa, techno
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the fan of house is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the prince-smoker##1
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the fan of salsa and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Cigar          | fonseca  | aristoff    | havana | prince       |
| Hobby         | writing | photography | chess  | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | techno      | house  | ambient     |

