.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, country, classical, funk
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, filmmaking, hiking, reading
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rabbit
1. the fan of funk is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the fan of classical and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of classical##1
4. the fan of r&b is the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the fan of funk is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | funk  | classical       | country   |
| Hobby      | drawing     | hiking | filmmaking | reading |
| Pet        | pony        | rabbit | ferret     | hamster |

