.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, fishing, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, police-officer, project-manager, security-guard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, january, march, august
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is the security-guard##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the paramedic and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the project-manager is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
7. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | fishing   | chess           | baking         | skydiving      |
| Job     | paramedic | project-manager | security-guard | police-officer |
| Birthday   | march     | january         | june       | august        |

